<h1>uService Demo</h1>

<p>Welcome to the uService Demo Weather Forecasts application!</p>

<p>This Blazor WebAssembly application demonstrates a microservices architecture with full CRUD operations for Weather Forecasts.</p>

<h3>Features:</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>List</strong> - View all weather forecasts</li>
    <li><strong>Search</strong> - Search weather forecasts by summary term</li>
    <li><strong>View</strong> - View detailed information about a specific forecast</li>
    <li><strong>Create</strong> - Add new weather forecasts</li>
    <li><strong>Update</strong> - Edit existing weather forecasts</li>
    <li><strong>Delete</strong> - Remove weather forecasts</li>
</ul>

